Yup.

I guess I am trying to be fair with the characters. In the Beast Wars
cartoon some characters were bigger than others. I think Basic was
about 5 feet tall or so while Ultra topped out at about 10.5 feet
tall. No one is really tall in Beast Wars except compared to each
other. Yes, Unicron is an obvious exception :)

Primal stood at about 10 feet tall and Megatron stood at 10.5 Leo
Prime was about 10 feet as well. Cheetor at about 7.5 and Rat Trap at
about 5. There is a video game that gives stats for a few characters
that I am going by as well as some of the web sites.

So the imported characters can have heights based on that. I would
assume that Tuscon, Rodimus and Hydras would all be about the same
height as their counter parts. Tuscon and Rodimus should be about the
same as Leo Prime and Optimus Primal, while Hydras should be about the
same height as Megatron.

Any ways it gives us something to think about :)

